snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Dawn of War IV – "Back to War" In-Engine Trailer | PC Gaming Show Tokyo Direct
snippet.description:
Here’s your official look into the next evolution of the iconic real-time strategy franchise with Warhammer 40,000: Dawn of War IV!
First revealed during PC Gaming Show: Tokyo Direct, this new trailer has been captured entirely from in-engine gameplay. 

Many years after the events of Dawn of War: Dark Crusade, Kronus burns as Space Marines of the Blood Ravens Chapter and their Adeptus Mechanicus allies clash with brutal Ork hordes. With victory almost certain, a new threat emerges: the Necrons. As this new faction overwhelms the battlefield, the Imperium must rebuild and grow their forces if they hope to stand a chance. 

Whether you’re a long-time fan of the series or brand new to the world of Dawn of War, this new trailer, captured entirely in-engine, provides a more detailed look at what to expect with exciting gameplay, action-packed cinematics, and a taste of the war-torn future that awaits.

At last, back to war! 
---

Warhammer 40,000: Dawn of War IV releases on Steam in 2026!

snippet.title: Golden Brothers 2 | Official Trailer (2025)
snippet.description:
| 🎥Në kinema prej datës 16 Tetor 2025🎥 | Një marrëveshje e thjeshtë. Një rol i përkohshëm. Një natë që ndryshon gjithçka.
Koli, një i burre i zakonshëm në një vend të huaj, futet në një lojë të rrezikshme ku realiteti dhe manipulimi përzihen. I ofruar nga Besi — mjeshtër i lojës së ndyrë dhe me një axhendë të fshehtë — ai pranon të luajë babanë e Nandit, një personazh misterioz me lidhje të errëta.
Por Koli s’e di se ky rol i çuditshëm do ta fusë në qendër të një rruge pa kthim, të mbushur me sekrete të së shkuarës, përballje me figura të errëta… dhe me Even — një grua enigmatike, më e rrezikshme seç duket e cila do te fus ne loje personazhe nga e kaluara e saj qe do te behen kercenim per Kolin dhe Besin.
Në këtë labirint emocionesh e rreziku, zbulohet se Mela, e dashura e Nandit, është vajza e Eves. Loja nuk është më vetëm për para apo për mbijetesë — por edhe për dashuri. Dashuri që lëndon, që përçan dhe që mund të kthehet në armë.
Midis intrigave, tradhtive dhe hakmarrjes, një gjë mbetet e padiskutueshme:
Besi nuk fal. Dhe gjithmonë e merr atë që i takon — qoftë para, nder apo gjak.

🎥Në kinema prej datës 16 Tetor 2025🎥

Një film nga Drilon Hoxha:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Official.Drilon.Hoxha
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/drilonhoxha
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@drilonhoxhaofficial

snippet.title: 《肥牛》晴天林｜荃灣火鍋放題貪心男女 生蠔肥牛蝦蟹乜都塞落袋（原曲：阿牛 - 陳奕迅）
snippet.description:
#火鍋放題 #肥牛 #陳奕迅

《肥牛》
原曲：阿牛 - 陳奕迅
改詞：梁栢堅 & 晴天林

一盤肥牛
職員嚟 即場拿出盤肥牛
可恨在 用隻手gel 埋油頭
經理看到咁大袋  才和我開口

埋單之前一刻才趕到
唔通有人通報才知道
這日任叫火鍋 叫咁大煲
怎能預計似這般  全入鏡全城望到
我哋打緊邊爐
開心到 當作入嚟尋寶

不甘心
尤其這紛爭   就像偷三牲
想過攞膠箱   我差點講真

成包生蝦早已將密實嘅袋去焗暈
再叫 十幾斤
份量足夠食飽四十人
約定日後 菜用嚟炆海蔘
拿來烚我尚有餘的冬粉
狂叫 再落海鮮七份
新鮮到 我再袋埋唐芹

好開心 袋住好開心
肥牛海鮮羹 返去滾一滾
不打緊
誰人不貪心 就是很貪心
拎了兩三斤  隻生蝦郁緊

執到寶
成包出前一丁拿得到
難得放題 拎晒來醫肚
往後自製生蝦蟹柳食譜
本來仲有更多的豬牛羊魚肉未到
最後拎啲生蠔
貪心到 叫我食神肥佬

很開心 袋住很開心
贈姨媽姑嬸 返去滾一滾
不打緊
誰人不貪心 就是很貪心
拎了兩三斤 又慳幾千蚊

一頭肥牛
走全場 收埋甜蝦和肥牛
慘淡在侍應影低我眉頭
一放上網即出名 點樣走
我食牛 我食牛

snippet.title: WEDNESDAY: SEASON 3 – First Trailer | Jenna Ortega, Lady Gaga | Netflix
snippet.description:
— Attention Viewers ⚠️
— This is a Fan-Made Concept Trailer for:
— WEDNESDAY: SEASON 3

— This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I’ve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support — now let’s dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. 🎬✨

— In this concept trailer for Wednesday Season 3, the story dives deeper into the gothic world of Nevermore as Wednesday Addams faces her most harrowing challenge yet. Enid Sinclair’s transformation into an Alpha werewolf sets Wednesday and Uncle Fester on a desperate search to bring her back, while Tyler Galpin wrestles with his Hyde nature and the dangerous pull of a rising pack. At the heart of the Addams family, long-hidden truths surface with the return of Aunt Ophelia, whose twisted past and ominous intentions threaten to tear the family apart. As Morticia and Gomez struggle to protect their daughter and Thing once again proves vital to survival, Wednesday must navigate a treacherous path of supernatural lore, fractured loyalties, and family betrayal. Season 3 promises to unearth the darkest secrets of the Addams legacy, with Wednesday standing at the center of a looming battle that could redefine her fate forever.

snippet.title: Minecraft LIVE - September 2025
snippet.description:
New game drops! Developers! More!

Minecraft LIVE is our own super special show that gives you the inside info on everything happening in the world of Minecraft! 

We’re updating vanilla Minecraft with multiple game drops per year, so we now host two of these shows to cover all the new features. Every episode includes fresh info from our developers, the inside scoop on unannounced upcoming game drops, and more! 

After the broadcast, stay tuned in for the Deep Dig After Show where our developers and guests show off the new features, often resulting in chaos. Vu Bui will return as host and attempt to keep things running smoothly. Good luck to that guy!

American Sign Language: https://www.youtube.com/live/W3uQA_unm0I
British Sign Language: https://youtube.com/live/ZygMYm2sx5U
Audio Descriptions: https://youtube.com/live/DoXrLv__PAY

Check out Minecraft.net for more information!  
https://www.minecraft.net/
